            <h2 class="section-title">Why we exist</h2>
            <div class="content-with-image-right">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <div class="story-content">
                        <p>Alphafox was founded on a simple but powerful belief: the gap between clinical excellence and digital experience is costing lives, deepening disparities, and undermining trust in healthcare.</p>
                        
                        <p>Too many patient portals frustrate the people they're meant to serve. Too many clinical tools slow down providers instead of supporting them. Too many health apps are abandoned because they don't fit into real lives.</p>
                        
                        <p>This isn't just about designâ€”it's about outcomes. When a medication reminder actually helps someone adhere to their treatment. When a telehealth interface makes care accessible to someone who couldn't otherwise receive it. When a provider spends less time clicking and more time connecting with patients.</p>
                        
                        <p><strong>That's the healthcare experience we're here to create.</strong></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
